title: From the Vault: The Origins of Numeracy
itunes:title: From the Vault: The Origins of Numeracy
description:
What are numbers and where does our number sense come from? Is numeracy an innate part of our biology, or is it a cultural invention? In this classic episode of Stuff to Blow Your Mind, Robert and Joe explore the origins of numbers. (originally published 6/15/2021)
